UML:TaggedValue.value: <u>DESCRIPTION:</u> This diagram shows the scope of a work package to be impacted as a part of a broader transformation roadmap. The enterprise context diagram links a work package to the organizations processes, and roles that will be added, removed or impacted by the project. This diagram is a valuable tool for understand the scope in context
